00:23:16,430 --> 00:23:20,850
That's... the estimated impact time.

230
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,410
Yes.

231
00:23:28,230 --> 00:23:30,690
What's going to happen to everything?

232
00:23:33,860 --> 00:23:37,450
Either way, I guess neither of us want to die.

